The document is intended as a standard reference guide that outlines the complete process assuming a dual-region setup, since that’s how most GovCloud applications are currently configured. For applications that run in a single region, the same steps would simply apply within that active region. The expectation is that the person performing the renewal is familiar with their app’s deployment pattern and can adjust accordingly.

